/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/polarized-israel-gaza-war-is-forcing-young-u-s-jews-to-choose-sides/0000018c-a608-db79-abee-f6ad3b1d0000</guid></item><item><title>从黎巴嫩向教堂发射的反坦克导弹造成九名以色列士兵和一名平民受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon-at-church-wounds-israeli-nine-soldiers-one-civilian/0000018c-a6ae-dd77-a59e-ffaf6d720000</link><description>一枚反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部巴勒斯坦基督教村庄的一座教堂大院，击中一名 80 岁的平民。以色列士兵赶到现场疏散他，却被另一枚导弹击中</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 16:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/anti-tank-missile-fired-from-lebanon-at-church-wounds-israeli-nine-soldiers-one-civilian/0000018c-a6ae-dd77-a59e-ffaf6d720000</guid></item><item><title>新总统米莱、阿根廷犹太人和以色列：一个棘手的三角关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-president-milei-argentinas-jews-and-israel-a-tricky-triangle/0000018c-a1fe-df1f-a7bf-b7ff05de0000</link><description>哈维尔·米莱赞扬了本杰明·内塔尼亚胡，并表示他正在考虑皈依犹太教。阿根廷犹太社区的许多人希望，如果新总统的自由主义思想失败，他们不会受到指责</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 16:16:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/new-president-milei-argentinas-jews-and-israel-a-tricky-triangle/0000018c-a1fe-df1f-a7bf-b7ff05de0000</guid></item><item><title>普京任命高级官员协助处理加沙人质问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/putin-appoints-senior-official-to-help-with-gaza-hostage-deal/0000018c-a67b-dbb4-af9f-ef7bdcbf0000</link><description>俄罗斯总统代表在莫斯科举行的一次会议上告诉以色列德鲁兹领导人，普京已经满足了内塔尼亚胡的要求，并任命副外长就此事采取行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 14:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-26/ty-article/.premium/putin-appoints-senior-official-to-help-with-gaza-hostage-deal/0000018c-a67b-dbb4-af9f-ef7bdcbf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政界人士称，带回约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦工人不在讨论范围之内</t